lead_paragraph: The grand jury will consider whether to charge Manziel, a quarterback for the Cleveland Browns, on allegations that he attacked his ex-girlfriend.

headline.print_headline: Police Refer Manziel Case to Grand Jury in Dallas
headline.main: Police Refer Manziel Case to Grand Jury in Dallas

snippet: The grand jury will consider whether to charge Manziel, a quarterback for the Cleveland Browns, on allegations that he attacked his ex-girlfriend.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Dallas Police Dept is referring domestic violence case against Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel to grand jury; Manziel could face up to one year in jail and $4,000 fine if case goes to trial; other football news noted.
